<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ وك:</span> <span class="c2">(التَّهَوُّكُ)</span> التَّحَيُّرُ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> « <span class="c2">(أَمُتَهَوِّكُونَ)</span> أَنْتُمْ كَمَا <span class="c2">(تَهَوَّكَتِ)</span> الْيَهُودُ وَالنَّصَارَى؟» ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْحَسَنُ:</span> مَعْنَاهُ مُتَحَيِّرُونَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>